Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 燃烧小宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧你的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧小宇宙…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙 让我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆发！！！
