Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:21:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 小宇宙
